<l>tuṟantār perumai tuṇaikkūṟiṉ vaiyat</l>
<l>tiṟantārai yeṇṇikkoṇ ṭaṟṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If one were to measure the greatness of ascetics, it would be</l>
<l>like counting all those who've passed upon the Earth.</l>
            </lg>
